Package: rzvec
Title: R Bindings for the zvec Vector Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bartek", "Szabat", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "keneo@szabat.com")
Description: Provides idiomatic R wrappers around the Python 'zvec' vector database
    library via 'reticulate'. Supports collection management, document CRUD,
    vector similarity search, and index management.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Python (>= 3.10), zvec Python package
Imports:
    reticulate
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
